                     <interp inst="t18310630-169-person1245" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I took the prisoner, and received this spoon from Mr. Vinton.</p>
               <p>MR. SPRATT. This is part of the spoon missed on the 12th - the other one has not been found.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. Chanor persuaded me to take my master's things, and when I took one he wanted to pursuade me to take another - he wanted me to take money out of the till.</p>
               <p>
